gears needed for your next challenge.   Have great adventures to explore the 'dark forest' where you may need to fight against mystery malicious creatures and collect treasures as a reward.   No one knows what risks you'll have to resolve till tomorrow\u2026", "short_description": "When rescue does not seem possible, can you survive along with the island? Crafting, hunting, farming, building to thrive on the island."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://fvworks.github.io/TillTomorrow/privacy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Self", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://fvworks.github.io/TillTomorrow/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "CASUAL", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "zh_CN"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1031637430756183"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 5, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1204104773940811"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "792472459069798"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "781565196727744"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "475083431090561"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "934707067217113"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "792472459069798"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1724684400, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1204104773940811"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "7867602883358279", "version": "0.8.0.6"}, "id": "1004118